file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: Entities
  version: '1.0'
paths:
  /:
    get:
      operationId: getRoot
      parameters:
        - name: color
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Color'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: ''
        '400':
          description: 'Invalid value for: query parameter color'
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    Color:
      type: string
      enum:
        - blue
        - red

Error: notImplemented: path "/": get: responses: 400: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
